casebody.data:
Wandajune Kearney v. Michael M. Kearney.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied, with $10 costs, and the time of the defendant to answer the complaint is extended until 20 days after service of a copy of the order, with notice of entry, upon the defendant. Concur — Peek, P. J., Botein, Prank, Yalente and McNally, JJ. [See ante, p. 903.]
